data.description: Taxes do not reflect a Homeowners Exemption, which will bring the taxes down to approximately $7036.74. Having a home owners exemption will bring your monthly payment down by approximately $147/mo and can be applied for once you purchase the home.   Seller is willing to pay your lender to bring your loan interest rate down by 1% for the first year. ($174/mo). This way you can keep your monthly payment low until the home owners exemption kicks in and reduces your taxes.  Homewood Flossmoor HS!! Beautifully updated and ready for new owners. Gorgeous new kitchen with quartz countertops, white shaker style cabinets and all stainless appliances. All new Flooring, including luxury vinyl plank flooring and all new carpet.  All new interior paint, fixtures and lighting. New furnace and water heater installed in August 2022. (per previous owner). Please view the 3-D tour and schedule your private showing TODAY! Please contact your attorney/broker/lender regarding details of the homeowners exemption and current taxes for the property.
